My wife remembered Nido from when she was a kid so we tried it out. Our experience is very positive. It tastes great and the kids love it. Now we make a gallon of milk when we run out -- no need to run to the store. The canister is giant; I haven't figured out exactly how much milk it makes, but its quite a bit -- off hand it seems like a better

title: Only thing better is fresh roasted on the boardwalk
description: This item is one of my periodic Sam's Club purchases. There's never been a bad pack in the bunch--something I can't say for all the convenience-store & vending machine competitors I've tried, such as Lance. The only thing consistently better than Planters packaged nuts is if you can get them still warm from the roaster (and that always makes me think of Planters, too, because of the shop near 8th Street on the boardwalk in Ocean City).

title: A cup of perfect
description: I look forward to this cup of Chai tea every evening.  It's PERFECT.  I actually like it better than what I previously paid 4 dollars for at THE coffeehouse.  It is creamy, sweet, and tasty.  I do recommend using a smaller keurig setting with it so it doesn't taste watered-down, but otherwise, it's seriously perfect.

description: These are a great value and it shows up right to the door. Great shipping time, too. The kids love them but I have to admit I do too.

description: We had company come from NY state for the holidays last year and they all wanted the "recipe" for this delicious soup.  We also did a fundraiser at work during November--outside and it was cold--so we decided to sell soup as an extra way to make money.  We sold every drop of this soup since word spread quickly for people to come over and buy a cup!

title: Bear Creek Chicken Noodle Soup mmmm goood
description:
This soup was purchased for an outdoor parking lot sale when we needed to have some warm weather food items to sell to customers. I made gallons of the soup and it all sold. Many people commented on how good it was and many went back to buy another cup.
Since it is lacking in chicken meat, I stewed some chicken beforehand and added it. adding the chicken meat seems to be the only thing that would make this tasty soup better!

title: We love this soup
description: Each winter, we stock up on Bear Creek dry soups.  We especially love the chicken noodle.  Sometimes I make it with half chicken broth and half water but it is so tasty it's as good with just water

title: Orbana gives you the lift you need to get out the door!
description: I have always looked to running as a special treat to selfishly do something that is just for me. My choice distance is the Marathon. Last year I ran Eugene and had a great race with a Boston Qualifying time of 3:27. My friend was visiting from London around the same time and gave me a sachet of Orbana to try. It was a cold and rainy morning and I didn't feel like running, but I mixed my Orbana into water and drank it down. As I got dressed I started to smile with anticipation of my run. Orbana

title: Love them!!!
description: This is a wonderful "cookie" that is very light and not too sweet.  Makes a lovely mid-afternoon or late-night snack.  Great service from the company.

title: Beautiful!
description:
I bought this bonsai as a Mother's Day gift. It arrived with tons of blooms on it, and is lovely. It is a bit bushy, unlike the picture, but I figure they ship it untrimmed in order to protect the blooms.
I'm very happy with the purchase!

title: Very satisfied
description: This soup is delicious. The grocery stores near me do not carry the low sodium soup so I as thrilled to find it on amazon.

title: My very favorite brand of Curry
description: I've tried other brands of "curry bars"  such as Golden, but Vermont Curry is just plain the best, by far. It's delicious.

title: Put it on everything!
description:
This is some of the finest hot sauce I've had. I highly reccomend putting it on pizza, breakfast burritos, steaks, chicken, everything.

Use a whole bottle in a crock pot with a pork roast to make some fine fine carnitas.

Buy it, you will not be dissapointed.

title: Brazil nuts
description: Dr. Oz suggested that there was a lot of health value in eating a few Brazil nuts every day. Following his advice, I purchased this product through Amazon.com. Most of the nuts are very tasty but every once in a while I came across one that tasted a bit moldy. Maybe that is the common nature of this nut and of course outside of the taste, I keep the extra supply in the freezer. I am enjoying having a good supply of these nuts for my good health. Shipping service was excellent.

title: amazon price
description: This is a great, healthy food. I have three cats that love all the flavors of this brand. That't why I gave it five stars.........BUT...the Amazon  price is outrageous. It's almost twice as much as most other places. For example, petfooddirect.com has this flavor, 24 3oz cans for $22.99 and they offer free shipping sometimes.

title: Refreshing
description: Sleepytime Exta helps you fall asleep naturally, and when you wake up in the morning you feel refreshed and ready to meet the day. No drousy or tired feeling. I recommend it highly.

title: Salt fish
description: Fish was sent very quickly and was fresh and still cold once it was deleivered. Greattatse and great for akee and saltfish dishes.

title: My favorite Pistachios
description: These are my favorite pistachios. They are always fresh and are crunchier than other brands, which is the way I like them. I have purchased these at least 10 times at Costco and have never been disappointed.

title: Ginger Honey tea granuals
description:
These are a staple in my pantry. I make a two litter bottle of green tea with one or two packets of the ginger honey tea added. I love the flavor and I don't get acid kick-back anymore. title: Must have product.
description: After using this product on 21 trees and several shrubs in my yard, the results are fantastic ! There is no way you can overdo it with this product. I use a wood stake and make a hole first inside the tree drip line, easy as pie.  If rain is low in your area , as it is in ours this year, make sure your trees get plenty of water. Thank you Miracle-Gro !

title: Good but not Great
description: Okay, I admit that I am a very serious chilihead so I wasn't expecting these to blow me away.  They definitely have a nice warmth to them, they were very fresh, and the flavor is very much that of a Slim Jim.  But yes, I wish they were much hotter.  Still, now that I've had one of these it will be very difficult to go back to any milder version.  I also wish they came in a shorter snack-size version.  Highly recommended to anyone who likes heat and Slim Jim.

title: Perfect Scoville Portability
description:
I've been using this spice for years and love it. The heat level lies somewhere between dried Habanero powder and dried Ghost Pepper powder. It should be used with caution and you should definitely wash your hands if sprinkled upon.

The best part of these bottles is that the glass is very thick and the plastic top is very strong and durable and most importantly air-tight. They won't break easily and the powder does not leak out. I carry one in the car and frequently one in my pock

title: I Really Missed These
description: These candies have become increasingly difficult to find in stores.  Glad to find them here at Amazon.  They're a wee bit smaller than the bits you find in the candy bar.  I prefer these because they're slightly cheaper per ounce and I don't feel obligated to eat six at a time like when you unwrap a new bar.  Although it is sometimes hard to resist opening just... one... more....

title: Gluten free, really? They taste AMAZING!!
description: Finding gluten free products that taste decent is a challenge and I bought a box of these cookies expecting them to taste "good" but still, with an off taste from being gluten free. Wow, was I wrong! These cookies are amazing!! They are shaped like animals, light, crunchy, buttery, and a hint of lemon. These are hands down the best cookies I've had in my life, including "regular" cookies, and this is the first time I can actually say a gluten free item tastes better than its gluten counterpart.<

title: Amazing Cookies!!
description:
Wow! I thought when I went gluten-free, I wouldn't be able to find any good chocolate cookies, but boy, was I wrong!
These cookies have the richest chocolate flavor I've ever tasted in my life. They fix my chocolate cravings within one bite, and one cookie is enough for me at a time because they are so rich and yummy! I would highly recommend these cookies to anyone, gluten-free or not!

Btw, I bought these at Wal-Mart for 3.30/box.

title: Delicious!
description: This is a delicious instant breakfast.  I ate the traditional Quaker Instant Oatmeal for years and cannot tell the difference but enjoy the benefit of less added sugar.  The problem is Amazon's price.  I can get this at Target and a couple of other stores for about $3 per box.  Why the premium?  I was looking for a discount.

title: Good Cookies
description: We have liked the Praeventia cookies but our local food stores no longer carry them.  We are very pleased to find this source of purchase.  The order was delivered on time and in excellent shape.

title: Healthy Supplement
description: We use this product each morning at breakfast time as an added source of essential Omega 3 and 6 along with helpful amino acids.  The supplier through Amazon provided easy ording process, saving us a trip to the local Health Food CO-OP.  Our order arrived in excellent shape and well before the anticipated delivery date.  The supplier's price is very competative compared to local venders.

title: Excellent Earl Grey
description: The main thing I like about Davidson's teas is that they are certified organic. I have been buying these teas from Amazon now for a few years and with their "subscribe and save" program you can get automated delivery at a reduced price and if you are a "Prime" member you get free shipping as well! The Davidson Earl Grey tea is to my taste very good and I have it automatically shipped to me at three month intervals. I highly recommend this tea and the Subscribe and save program!

title: South African Honeybush is a hit!
description: What I really like about the South African Honeybush tea is the gently sweet taste and wonderful fragrance. I often blend it with other teas I have but most often brew it straight by itself to enjoy the really great aroma and flavor.

title: Earl Grey with more flavor
description: I like the fact that Davidson's teas are certified organic. The Earl Grey with lavender is a bit more bitter than standard Earl Grey but to my taste buds that is just fine. It is a flavorful tea that I enjoy often.....especially at breakfast.

title: Cute lil bottles
description: These bottles are cute, I thought I was getting bottles like the pic, which was a lil confusing, like am I really getting cheated, lol, but overall, great product and of course I like the juice.

title: Big Hit
description: My dogs absolutely love these. I've tried the maple & sweet potato and the apple versions.  They especially love them after a walk. When I ask them if they want a "freezy pup", they know what I mean and run to the fridge! I highly suggest them. I bought a regular ice tray and don't fill them completely up. I can get 12 per pack.

title: Easily the best low cal no sugar mix I've had
description:
I was looking for something without sugar/carbs as far as a mix and I finally found it. Scales Margarita Mix is by far the best I've tasted. We've tried multiple others (including the horrible Skinny Girl drinks) and this is the only one that doesn't taste like it's low cal or leave a bad after taste.

My only complaint is the shipping price from most of the sellers. It may be worth buying if you buy multiple bottles but otherwise I'm going to try and find this locally.

title: Good variety and you can easily make it 0 cal with Splenda
description:
As another reviewer has mentioned you can make this calorie free by using Splenda instead of sugar which is exactly what we do. We always keep a pitcher of Kool Aid with Splenda in the fridge when you want something "sweet" but don't want to drink down a couple hundred calories. It's a great guilt free way to satisfy that craving.

For those reviewers saying the cost is too high: Each packet makes about 64 oz. 64oz x 48 packets = 3072 oz. By my math thats the equivalent of 153 20o

title: Great quick and tasty snack
description: These are a great snack in between meals or on the go.  They are low in calories, high in whole grains, and taste good.  My only complaint is I haven't seen a big variety pack so some people might get sick of the flavor buying 48 of the same type.  Personally I haven't but I usually rotate my morning snack between this or a piece of fruit.

title: Great, Easy to make and NO Calories!
description:
Yes, the noodles does have fishy smell when you open it. However, it goes away once you start running against hot water for a minute or two.
Though tasteless, the noodle, absorbs flavor thus making it tastier than the actual noodle.

title: McIlhenny
description: Great product for pre-fab. Almost as good as the recipe that takes me a while to put together. I add a little Tabasco Habenero, squeeze of lime, and off we go! Consider a splash of dry sherry to smooth things out. Be safe.

title: Addictive!
description: Oh. My. Gawd! This is the most delicious, addictive chocolate I have ever eaten. I will be ordering TONS more of this!

title: Taste great!
description: I stopped in the Cayman Islands and fell in love with this rum cake. It makes a great gift too.

title: Wonderful product.
description: This is a great product. I wish it were easier to find in local stores. Thank goodness for the internet.

title: Wonderful after-tang
description:
I confess I like my orange marmalade bitter, and the edge of bitterness you get with this marmalade is quite perfect. It's not overwhelming but very present, and the titillating taste lingers. I find this complex flavor highly civilized and incontrovertibly British.

Marmalade requires a lot of sugar in the making, but this marmalade gives us 47g of fruit per 100g, according to the label. For marmalade, that's pretty good. The color is definitely tawny, neither too dark nor too light.

title: Works for me
description:
I don't know what the magic ingredient might be (perhaps fennel?), but I always feel better after drinking this tea when I have a stomachache or intestinal disturbance.

Yogi is good at imparting complexity to its teas, and Stomach Ease has a pleasing blend of flavors. There is a medicinal tang to it, but that's nice when you want some healing action. The flavor is so good, I sometimes drink it when I'm feeling fine, just for fun.

All the ingredients are organic: licorice ro

title: I'm drinking it as I write
description:
I hope you'll buy this tea. I want it to be extremely popular, so Yogi will never discontinue it. I'm crazy about it and drink it after dinner every night.

I drink high-test Japanese green tea in the morning and herb tea at night. It's hard to find an herbal tea that doesn't seem wimpy after my intense green tea buzz. Yogi Aztec Sweet Chili tea is the herbal tea I've been looking for all my life - mysteriously full-bodied and satisfying.

It's made from organic spices that w

title: Takes me back to London
description:
It's been a while since I visited England, but this taste brings it all back: the clipped speech, the full-bodied tea and the bitter, bitter marmalade. If you're looking for a mild, laid-back marmalade, this is not it. The color is seriously dark, and the flavor of the coarse-cut Seville oranges is intense.

I wouldn't use this marmalade for baking sweet muffins, but it will grace a piece of toast with majesty and reward every bite. The label says this marmalade is for the mature palat

title: Cat Fisher Garden Mitt
description:
I liked this toy but my cat did not. It seemed well made and well thought out. The fingers have stiff plastic tubes that keep the actual toys away from your hand so the cat does not scratch your hand. There are elastic strings that keep the toys attached while allowing the cat to tug and play with each toy. The toys theyselves are adorable little insects that are actually pretty large.

description: I haven't bought this order, but I received a tin of these mints as a present and they are the greatest. these tiny mints have an incredibly full and sweet berry flavor that gets me through the day at work! Would be so cute for a party!

description: I think one review is enough if my cat likes it I will buy her it again. I will say it again I think one review is enough if my cat likes it I will buy her it again.

description: I went from drinking milk, (to much fat content), to drinking ice tea. I was going to store to often for it so I decided to purchase two case of it and now its time to order more.

description: Nice!  Great for after coffe or meals.  Makes your mouth feel clean and refreshed!!

title: Smooth and powerful
description: I first tasted this coffee as a sample with my new Keurig.  It wasn't available locally, so I tried Emeril's.  The Newman's own is really just as strong, but MUCH SMOOTHER.  It's delicious, and by far the best I've tried so far.

title: my 3 dogs love,love,love it
description: my 3 dogs love,love,love it.  I have 2 large, and one small dogs, and they can't get enough of it.  I only gave a 4 star, because, my one large dog devours it within 3 minutes,then barks at the other dogs for not sharing.  I end up having to sneak another to him (I have to sneak or the other dogs, despite them already having one, wants another), just to shut him up. I definitely  would recommend it to dog owners.

title: Wonderful!!!!!!!!!
description: I've bought the Lady Grey teabags for years and enjoyed them...However, the loose tea is even better!!!  It is not as harsh as the Earl Grey but with a more subtle citrus flavor.  This has been a favorite of mine for years and hopefully for years to come.  (Twinings--please don't ever discontinue this flavor...It is superb!)

title: Wonderfully Yummy product!
description: This mix is wonderful both by itself and if you add a tea bag to the cup making it a "cider and tea" beverage.  It's nice to have something that diabetics can enjoy without the guilt.  Love this and will continue to buy it!

title: Unbelievable!
description: My husband and two of our close friends actually fight over this stuff, they love it that much.  It has become a contest to see who has more packets, who drinks them faster....etc.

title: It's good stuff
description:
Not a miracle but, in my experience there is no such thing when it comes to these drinks. I will say that does seem to give a mental lift and I really like the taste, it's different.

I'd probably buy it a lot more often if it cost less. I wouldn't mind drinking one of these every day but even with free shipping $44 is not much cheaper than the average $2 a can it usually goes for at the store. Pricey for 8.4 ounces.

title: Excellent Tea for Two or One
description: This is excellent tea for anyone using a Keurig machine.  The perfect cup of tea for one or two people.  Easy to store, easy to use and easy to dispose of.

title: LOVE this product!
description: No more mixing packets into cold drinks and seeing it settle in the bottom!  I use EZ sweets in hot, cold drinks, and cooking and baking.  This product earns it's high rating!!!  Look at per serving price vs. Splenda packets.

title: Cost
description: I love this stuff.. I keep it in my car, at home, and in the office. Even keep one in my Gym Bag. Used to be 7 bucks cheaper here. Price went up. Buy at Walmart $3.48 each there. 13.92 before Tax.

title: vegie meats
description:
Worthington Vegetable Steaks are nutritious, versatile and very tasty. I use them as "steaks", can be dipped in batter and pan fried. Use in stir fry, strip into pieces, and add to stir fry recipe. Yummy,as is, in a sandwich.
Give them a try! : )

title: Restaurant rice at home.
description: RiceSelect Royal Blend is my favorite rice.  It's like rice you'd get in a fancy restaurant, but you can make it easily at home in about 20 minutes. Per cup of rice, I add a tablespoon of chicken soup base to the rice water and the result is perfection every time. Try Royal Blend and I'll bet it becomes your favorite rice too.

title: Great Entertainment
description: My 1 year old Border Collie absolutely loves it! It's hard to keep him entertained and this tug-a-jug worked like a charm. I was also amazed that he wasn't able to destroy it....always a plus in my book. [...]. I would recommend to any owner looking for entertainment for their dog.

title: I'm picky and I pick Jeremiah's Pick
description:
My friend Don gifted me with a bag of Jeremiah's Pick Coffee Fogbuster whole bean coffee. I figured that HUGE, 5-pound bag would last me forever. NOT! Not when I tasted how GOOD was this coffee. I brewed many a pot and shared beans with family and friends. Then I bought a bag from Don and kept on drinking and sharing. Now I have my own amazon.com account.
This coffee is strong without being bitter; a nice, full-bodied flavor enhanced only by a splash of heavy cream. Mmmmmmm, heavenly!

I took my first sip and i knew the brown nectar of the gods had hit my taste buds with one million blasts of delicious flavor. WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO WHEN I DRINK ALL OF THIS PEPSI!??!? I'll have to buy more!! One of the best purchase I've ever made.

title: Great food and free shipping from Petco through Amazon
description:
We've fed our dog the Nutro line since she was a puppy. She's been on the Ultra line since they started making that 5 or 6 years ago. It's kept her coat very shiny even now that she's a senior.

Note: I'm not sure if this is a limited time offering, but the pricing of this food is cheaper on Amazon and shipping is free compared to directly from Petco.

title: Clear Men Scalp Therapy
description:
This shampoo met my expectations. I have very thick hair, and this shampoo leaves your hair fairly soft and smooth. It also smells very pleasant.

I use Head & Shoulders regularly, but I tried this product as an alternative. So far, it is very good - I still notice very minor flakes, but overall it has done a good job of keeping dandruff to a minimum.

I would consider purchasing this product again, I really like it.

title: Excellent
description: The soy milk is great.The price is comparable to the grocery store, but getting a dozen boxes at a time means we don't have to go to the store every other day.

title: Love it!
description: My husband and I love this stuff!  We tried it for the first time about 10 years ago at a small steakhouse in central California.  We have kept it in our fridge ever since.  We used to be able to buy it in the grocery stores in California, but since moving to Arizona we now purchase it online.  We love it with grilled New York steaks.

title: another great gourmet flavor
description: This French Vanilla brand is more intense than the rest of the competitors out there. I've tried several but this is the best French Vanilla.

title: another great gourmet flavor
description: This French Vanilla brand is more intense than the rest of the competitors out there. I've tried several but this is the best French Vanilla.

title: Bob's Red Mill Baking Soda 16-Ounce (Pack of 4)
description:
Two of the bags were leaking baking soda when I opened the box, but it was a very small amount. The thin plastic bag packaging could be improved upon. I transferred the baking soda from those two bags into a glass Ball Jar.

The quality of the Baking soda is very good. It is a much finer grain, than regular Arm & Hammer baking Soda, so it is great for using in the homemade toothpaste I make using baking soda and coconut oil. I give the quality of the baking soda 5 stars.

title: So cute!
description: I got this plant on a whim. Im sure glad I did. The plant is compact and cute. Its very healthy and was packaged very well. Im just so pleased.

title: Love this stuff!
description: I ordered this after having much success with their liquid products. It is not bitter at all and has a very fresh/clean taste to it.  I have baked with it, used it on the stove, and in my oatmeal and hot cocoa.  When I run out, I'll be ordering more!

title: Tasty, especially the orange ones.
description:
These are pretty good little gummies. Suprisingly sweet. They do get hard after about 20 days, so don't order more than you need.

Great, tasty product.

title: Cola lover
description: Good product. Ideal if you want to make your cola a little stronger tasting for a quicker picker upper. A little pricey but good.

title: Great stuff, and smells nice too!
description: I was pleasantly surprised how lightweight this oil is and how quickly it absorbs in to my skin.  I also cook with it a little and it isn't too strong, although I keep thinking I smell like a large macaroon after I rub this in to my hands and arms. (It fades in a few minutes)  I've started giving it to my very old and very finicky cat, who to my surprise and delight, enjoys licking it off my fingers after she eats her dinner.  Her digestion has improved and it helps her keep a little weight on.

title: Yummy Granola Bars...
description: I don't understand the negative review as these are the closest thing to homemade granola that you can get.  They are dense, chewy and full of oat, nut and date flavor. I think there is batch variation as some have been tougher than others.  Perhaps that is why the other review called them "greasy". I find them very satisfying for breakfast and they aren't sugary sweet like commercial granola bars you buy in upermarkets.

title: Salty or Not
description: How many milligrams of salt are in each serving? I'm giving it all five stars to make up for the mistake made by someone else.

title: it doesnt smell like urine
description: i got this tea at wal-mart. it does smell odd but it is a fruity smelling oddness and not a urine type smell however it is quite as intense. anyway, if u don't judge it by the somewhat pleasant and at the same time somewhat offensive aroma, it does taste really good.

title: GOOD PIES
description: this was great the berries were very big and 3 cans per pie and we love them the receipe was on the can and it is a good one I will be ordering more!!

title: Yummy to the tummy, ouch to the pocketbook
description: I absolutely love this stuff but yowza it is expensive.  It is great for lunches and meals where the family is eating real Lasagna.

title: Go cocktails. Margaritas.
description: I have been doing low carb. These are great. I can finally have a drink that tastes great without feeling quilty. Thanks

title: Great Coffee!
description: I love chicory coffee and when I found tht Community Coffee makes these pods for my coffee machine, I bought two boxes. We finished them in two weeks! My guests also loves this coffee too!

title: Great for strong chewers
description:
Our dog is a very strong chewer and we are always looking for something that is safe for her to chew, but will keep her interest for extended time. Tried the reindeer antlers and she enjoys them, but once they have been chewed on she loses interest. Not so with the moose chew. She chews on it until she gets tired. There have been no sharp edges or shards to injure her. I bought a 2-pack to try and the first one has lasted a few days now.
They are expensive compared to rawhide or pig ears,

title: Vegan, fairly-priced, and comparable to my favorite ginger snap brand
description:
I'm a fan of ginger snaps and cookies. I can't have dairy, so I give a thumbs up to Newman's for making them vegan.

I always think twice about ordering food through the mail since fragility often leads to damages. Mine arrived in great condition and the bag and snaps weren't crushed. These are fairly-priced too, which is a great deal for organic food. Sometimes organic stuff is just "too rich for my blood," but not in this case. I'm giving you the green light to order!

title: Strong and Smooth, Top-notch Flavor
description: I like strong coffee. If you can see light through the coffee, it's too weak for me. After trying a couple dozen various K-cups from other suppliers, Emeril's Big Bold Easy stands out from the crowd. It is everything advertised: Big (strong), Bold (great flavor), and Easy (not bitter at all). Another reviewer mentioned Newman's Own Extra Bold, which is also good, but for me, Emeril's wins without contest.

So now i watch for a good price at Amazon and we buy it by the case. Make sure it is the GOLD ...

title: Yum!
description: So smooth, awesome price here.  Makes me want to get out of bed in the morning!  Definitely not your average coffee.

title: Low-Carb dieters Life Saver!
description: Substitute this delicious low-carb tortillas anywhere you use bread. I love hot dogs, but instead of a bun these days I melt some cheese on one of these (or the other regular carb-balance tortilla) squirt some mustard on it and wrap it around a cooked frank.  Satisfies the craving with very few carbs.

title: Where is Diet MD Code Red
description:
This was absolutely the best tasting diet soda on the market. It was like having a sumptious dessert. Everyone, please contact Pepsi and ask them to bring it back. Maybe consumer demand will spur it's reintroduction.
I only have one small suggestion for this product. Figure out a way to increase its viscosity slightly, and it will be even better.

title: wonderful!
description: I have loved Kashi cereal for years and recently found these bars, which are like some of the other cereal bars (NutriGrain?) I have had in the past, but from everything I can tell, seem to be of better quality. I think they work great as a snack or a quick breakfast. Better than a candy bar, but not as good a the raw fruit! :)

title: they grow on you!
description: Saw these in Whole Foods and thought they looked interesting. Didn't care for them instantly, but by the time the first bag as gone (I have a husband and kids), I was hooked. Wanted to try other flavors and this is a great way to do it. Personally, I like the plain and also the salt/pepper. My kids love all of them though and, while these aren't fruit/veggies, I feel better about giving these to them as opposed to standard chips.

If i like it, then your kids will like it, i've been looking for this product as in a box for years on amazon and i could not find it. It is also very economical to keep on hand instead of having to toss out soured milk in liquid form that I didn't need.  It also comes in a easy-to-use package.

description: I ordered this since my pediatrician recommended carrots and peas for my 7 month old who has been having rice cereal and bananas for a couple of months now. We tried the carrots and my baby loved it so much he finished about 3/4th of the 2 oz jar. However carrots are constipating and I had to give him 6 oz of apple juice mixed with water a day to relieve the constipation. title: Easy to make and tasty

title: easy to use agar
description: It works as well as agar in bar form and the price is good. I do however recommend you use half the recommended amount, so more like 1 tablespoon to 1 pint of liquid versus 2 tablespoons, but you might have to experiment and it will depend on the liquid. But 2 tablespoons I find will make it too stiff.

title: MmmmmmmMaple....

I would definitely buy again. I may have to use a little more than my normal dose, but not by much. I have even used this flavoring in my coffee!

title: great chili

I usually add ground hamburger meat to it. Love it, so when I saw that amazon carried this I was thrilled, now I can always have it on hand! Thanks Amazon!

title: Buy locally.  MUCH better deal.
description: Buy these locally if you can.  The local store was reorganizing and the place was such a mess that I couldn't locate the product when I needed to, so I tossed several into an Prime order that i was placing.  I ended up paying twice the price. :-(  Pretty bad deal really except the the actual product is excellent and much better than the MSG laced garbage from other bullion manufacturers that comes mostly in dry cubes.

I will say that she doesn't have any digestive problems (other than the occasional gross noise here and there, but I could say the same about myself).  So I didn't notice any issues before or after, which is fine by me.

Thank you...Fancy Feast...for such wonderful food~

title: Healthy mufins but the instruction is wrong
description: I am on a diet and would like to find a healthy yet delicious muffins as I am a muffin lover. I love this product. It is exactly what I wanted! But the instruction is wrong. It says to bake at 400 degree for 27mins. I did and found the muffins are hard and dry. I changed to 350 degree and add 2 whole eggs instead egg white and milk instead of water. It is delicious!

title: Rereview
description: I love this product that is why I order it.  I live in Medford, Oregon and can buy it at the Food 4 Less.  I am in California for 3 months and cannot find it anywhere.  So I have had to order it through Amazon.com.  The first time I ordered it the company I ordered from took well over a week to get it to me.  This company got it to me in 5 days.  So originally I was upset with them for taking 3 days to ship.  But it only took 2 days to get here.  Thank you.

title: Real Cookie Flavor
description: Unlike many store-bought gluten free baked goods, which have industrial appearances and oily textures, these look and taste like actual cookies.  They have a rich cocoa flavor, with real chocolate chips that crunch pleasantly between the teeth, and a soft but not squishy texture reminiscent of Mom's home-baked brownies.  Even our household's gluten eaters love them.  This is the dessert we've been looking for ever since my household went gluten-free.

title: Hits the Energy Drink Trifecta
description:
I work graveyard shifts, so I often need a boost of energy, but many energy drinks taste to me like a spoonful of sugar and the can they came in. Not this one, which actually tastes like a cherry soda. Its pleasing flavor goes down smoothly when I need quick power, and it doesn't leave an aftertaste like Full Throttle or Red Bull do. I could almost drink this like an ordinary beverage.

title: Tasty, Spicy, but Not Hot
description:
I keep a can of this poppable snack on my desk to nibble when I need a quick boost of spicy, crunchy goodness. Just a few, slammed back like popcorn, have enough punch to open my eyes and get my mind back on the work. The peas themselves have a light flavor, neither bland nor overpowering, that really carries the kick of the wasabi.

title: Mild but Sophisticated

Despite its sophisticated use of spices, the flavor is mild enough for newcomers unaccustomed to Indian food. title: Childhood favorite
description: I grew up with these drinks even though I live on the East coast of the US. I used to go to Hawaii in the summers and my family stopped at local stores to buy tropical drinks. Hawaiian Sun has always been one of my favorite drinks and Lilikoi Passion is especially delicious! I am so happy it's offered on Amazon for those of us who live far away.  Any Hawaiian Sun product is worth trying but this and the Pass-O-Guava are truly the best drinks on the planet.

title: Amazing!!!!
description: I love them! My whole family does! I have been eating them since I was young. The are so wonderful and such a great source of protein. I am so happy Amazon has them. Please keep them.. they are hard to find! Try these.. you will be very satisfied.

description:
Caribou makes a series of coffees; my current favorite is Mahogany. However, this, too is nice on the palate. The package describes the taste thus: "Caribou blend begins with a delightful heaviness on your palate and finishes with a relaxing balance of bittersweet chocolate and fruity flavors."

For tree huggers and environmentalists, Caribou--as a company--is a member of the Rainforest Alliance, designed to "protect ecosystems and the people and wildlife that depend on them. . . ."

title: Nice change of pace
description:
Do you love hamburgers? Do you feel guilty about the fat and cholesterol of beef patties? Here's a suggestion--try bison burgers.

More and more farmers are raising bison for their meat. It has less fat and cholesterol than beef, but it tastes pretty good! When making bison burgers, the key thing to remember is that they are quite a bit leaner than beef burgers, so you can't cook it as long or it really dries out.

title: What a nice snack!!

The pluses: sodium is relatively low; fiber is pretty good. Down side? A bit more saturated fat than I would like.

But this tastes good. It is a lot better than fried snacks.

Overall, I'm a satisfied customer.

title: Great product. Try making your own.
description:
This is a terrific product and about as healthy as you can get.

If you're a bit ambitious you can also make your own brown rice flour at a much lower price by grinding up uncooked brown rice in a powerful blender (like a Vitamix in the dry container) until the right consistency. Use the pulse mode, however, so it doesn't get hot during the grinding process. Can do the same with oats, white rice, whole wheat, tapioca, etc.

title: Great taste!

description: This chili sauce is like franks red hot, but its thicker and has more garlic taste to it. Trust me if your a hot sauce fan like i am, then deffinatly try this. Its a little hotter than Franks, but its not atomic. This sauce has more flavor than Franks. Do yourself a favor and just try this out, i guarentee you will love it as much as i do. Enjoy :)

title: Forgotten food of my youth.
description: Like another review, I remember these growing up and forgot about them.  I recently found them at the grocery store discounted because they are no longer carrying them.  I looked on Google and found them on Amazon at a great price with no tax.  I purchased just  enough that I didn't pay shipping either.  I am now stocked up and they will keep well.  I love them and they are great for a low calorie diet.

title: Just the Cheese mini rounds
description: These are great--very satifying. I got hooked on them before I became gluten-free, and especially appreciate them now.

title: Just the Cheese mini rounds
description: These are great--very satifying. I got hooked on them before I became gluten-free, and especially appreciate them now.

title: Delicious!
description: This coffee is delicious.  It smells like heaven.  The taste is not too overwhelming.  We will always have it on hand from now on!

title: Jamaican Canned Ackees
description: I certainly enjoyed the ackees.  I am originally from Jamaica, and missed the food at times.  This hit the spot for me.  Thanks very much.  I will purchase many mnore

title: Good "to go" snack for small kids
description: Our 2 year old son is affected by Celiac disease and since his diagnosis we have had a difficult time finding snacks that are easy to take out on a play date or to a park.  The "Glutino Apple Cinnamon Rings" serve that purpose very well for us and he LOVES them.  They don't taste like your typical cereal that contains flour - of course they don't.  But for someone who is on a gluten free diet and is accustomed to way the way that processed gluten free food tastes, these are a great, quick snack.

title: Two servings
description: This product is great to keep on hand for a light lunch that's quick and easy.  My husband and I both enjoy a mug of hot soup a couple of times a week, and this serves us nicely (we both tend to have lighter appetites).  It has a good consistency, is packed with tasty ingredients, and there is plenty of chicken.  One selling point is the terapack.  After learning about BHPA-containing can liners used by many soup manufacturers I decided we needed to avoid the ubiquitous stuff whenever possible.

title: Pantry Staple
description: Our family has always enjoyed this one-dish meal.  I keep a bag of broccoli florettes in the freezer and usually toss in a handful.  The vegetables cook up nicely and lend color as well as a bit more flavor.

title: These five-star cookies contain only four ingredients!
description: Wheat flour, butter, sugar, salt.  These are delicious, and are practically health food given this short list.  The attractive tin makes a nice hostess gift.

title: good stuff
description: My boyfriend brought me several small bags of Haribo gummy bears from Germany recently. These are the same and are good. I was going to have him get me a big bag the next time he went over, but now I don't have to... he can bring chocolate now!

title: Begging for more!!!!
description: My dogs love this food!!!  at times i see them picking out the dried veggies in this mix and eating those first....Kinda Funny!  well before i started my dogs on this food.... they were having some really bad gas problems.... They would stink me out of a room.... when they started eating this one.... No more Stinky gas!!!

title: The tastiest flour I've had for ages
description: Most affordable gluten free flours are made from rice, corn or soy. Those flours these tend to taste rather bland. Oat flour brings back some of the old flavor and is more nutritious than rice, corn or soy flour. I use it in almost all of my recipes, I love it!

title: Best Rice
description: This is best rice I found in America.  Taste so good like I ate in Japan. My daughter loved too. She said she will order for herself.

title: great coffee
description: Great coffee-doesn't bother my stomach at all.  A treat!  Thank you for the great product. I will order this product again.

title: Good product
description: We feel comfortable with this product and our baby likes it and has had no issues with it since we began feeding it to her eight months ago.

description: We feel comfortable with this product and our baby likes it and has had no issues with it since we began feeding it to her eight months ago.

title: Great Flavor
description: I had found these seeds at a convenience store several years ago and hadn't found them since in any store. Finally thought to check Amazon and what would you know. These seeds have a flavor that is just unbeatable and at a great price.

title: Easy to use
description: This sprouter is easy to use and small quantities can be sprouted.  With several small chambers, I can have fresh sprouts constantly.  I really like this product and use it all the time.

title: you want your fruit tree to produce for you
description:
get these fruit spikes shove them in the ground around not to close are the fertilizer will burn the tree, 2-3 ft around the tree i use 3 spikes on each tree i step on them water than watch the blooms just be patient And water

enjoy

title: LOVE, LOVE, LOVE
description: I can't say enough about the Flavrz drink mix concentrate Cherry Berry.  Nice addition to water in a restaurant.  You can save money on drinks by carrying these packets in your purse.  You decide what strength you want depending on how much water you add the concentrate to.  Great way to get water in kids just a little sweet but not too sweet.  Certainly better than all the sugary drinks and juices out there.  I will try other flavors of Flavrz.

title: GREAT treat and easy way to add healthy fat to your diet!
description: This is one of my family's favorite little indulgences, except that it's good for us! Coconut has many benefits but most of all fat in your diet gives you energy and helps you stay full for longer! This is delicious just plain off of the spoon, with fruits, in a smoothie, in sauces, or my favorite over a nice, hot, roasted sweet potato!

title: Love Them!
description: I didn't realize that "mini" crawlers meant the very small ones (maybe an inch or so big?), but I'm actually happier that they are! I thought these were the ones just a little bigger (about twice as big, in the regular packages in the stores)... but these are absolutely perfect. I love them, and they make a perfect reward treat for my potty training little boy, and for a fun reward for helping for my twin 4 year olds. The package is big, so make sure you have a ziploc bag (or two) handy to put t

title: These are the BEST prunes on the market.
description: I love prunes - I have eaten them daily for several years.  These prunes are the juiciest - although pricey!  They are worth it to me.

title: Great product!!
description: Love being able to use my own espresso!!  Easy to use!!  Fill with espresso, tamp down and put on lid.  Much cheaper than nespresso caps.

title: Kitty Yum Yum :0)
description: My cat, PONCHO, loves this food. He's one of those especially finicky cats too. The food is not overprocessed and sure to please the most particular of cats. Overall, a gourmet cat food at a reasonable price. Meow.

title: Excellent Organic Red Chai
description: Lovely red hue, spicy flavor, great price, via Amazon's subscribe and save. It's a real pick-me-up kind of tea and tastes lovely iced as well with a splash of organic agave nectar. Amazon's price is cheaper than my local grocers too. If you like Chai, check this out.

title: Great Dog Treat
description: My dog LOVES Lickety Stik in the bacon flavor. Since she likes it so much, I plan on getting the other flavors too. It's a great liquid treat for your dog. I highly recommend Lickety Stik.

title: Great, All-Natural Dog Treat
description: My dog loves these. They are a bit pricey, yet worth it for a special snack. I'm sure your dog will love them.

title: Great Dog Treat
description: My dog LOVES Lickety Stik in the bacon flavor. Since she likes it so much, I plan on getting the other flavors too. It's a great liquid treat for your dog. I highly recommend Lickety Stik.

title: Excellent but less juice than described
description:
The flavour is excellent and I would suggest it to anyone who has been disappointed with the typical apple juice flavour.

Be aware however, that you will be only getting 24 glass 16-Ounce bottles when you order, not the 20-Ounce ones as stated in the item description.

title: Love it BUT!! Too expensive on Amazon
description: So far this is my fav. HOWEVER. if i were to buy direct from Nespresso the 50 capsules would only be $32.50

title: Bar Harbor Indian Pudding
description: This product used to be carried by the Vermont Country Store.  We are grateful to be able to order this product on Amazon.  This product is well made and fun to used during the Holiday season.

title: Nice blend of seasoning and thickener
description: This provides a nice instant way to put together chili without a lot of bother. Normally, I like to cook from scratch but when I'm on a ski trip, I find these packets really helpful. I made a variation of this a few times using the crockpot and it was a huge hit. Highly recommend.

title: Love These
description: I got these originally for the convenience of the 8 oz containers. I find that because of the smaller containers, I'm using the broth more often in my cooking. This broth is very tasty, smooth on the tongue. Just throw in a few wontons and you have dinner. I was purchasing the 32 oz containers before and throwing away too much. With a household of two, these are perfect.

title: satisfaction guaranteed
description: I like a cereal, whether for breakfast or a late snack, that that's a bit of "work" to eat, has a nice flavor and lasts till the next real meal. This one delivers! It is a nutty, grainy taste, slightly sweet and a very satisfying texture. It stays solidly crunchy to the last bite. LOVE it, and the best part is how it's organic and healthful. Try this, and you'll never go back to Wheaties again. I only wish Amazon would post the Nutrition Facts (right from the product label) on every such food pr

title: Worth it!
description: My milk supply was good for everyday feedings, but I needed to start stocking up for going back to work. This did the trick! Highly recommend!

title: Best value
description: We go through Pamela's like crazy.  Fantastic for pancakes (we like to add a little vanilla to batter).  It also makes great chocolate chip cookies and banana bread.  The 25 lb bag is definately the best way to go value wise.

title: Makes drinking water so much easier!
description: I like True Lime very much, better than True Lemon and True Grapefruit. It is not overpowering, and gives just the right amount of zing.  I bought this large box because I need to drink water and it is so easy to just grab a few packets and put them in my purse to take to a restaurant and not have to worry about lemons in your water that may have been cut up with a contaminated knife!

title: Chocolate covered awesomeness in a bag!
description: A friend brought a bag of these for me from Costa Rica and I immediately fell in love with them! They are sweet and the dark chocolate really compliments the passion fruit. Great product all around!

title: Perfect
description:
It's a piece o heaven that fell on my plate.
It's rich, flavorfull, perfection for me!
I'm really in love with these brownies.

title: Yummy, but a little dry.
description: There aren't many cookies I don't like, so I may not be as objective as some people, but this cookie has great flavor. The only complaint I have about these Gooey Megafudge cookies is that they are a little dry. Nothing a little milk can't take care of though!

title: Excellent!
description: We LOVE this stuff! It is a little too sweet for our tastes when mixed as directed. So, we brew our regular coffee and add a couple of tablespoons to it that way. ADDICTIVE! Highly recommend.

title: The best roasted peanuts I've ever had!
description: These are without a doubt, the best roasted peanuts I have ever eaten! I don't know how they do it, but they are amazingly crunchy and highly addictive. My only suggestion would be to reduce the salt a bit, but other than that...man! Talk about good!

title: Crunchy and yummy!
description: These get an A+ from our crew. They were yummy and crunchy with whole grain nutrition. At first glance, they looked a little "earthy" with the crushed oat pieces on top. But, they really have great flavor and hold a somewhat nutritious balance. Great snack for the young and old at our house. I will buy these in the future!

title: Crispy and flavorful
description: This Shake 'n Bake was really yummy. It made the chops crispy without adding all of the fat. The flavor was delicious without being overbearing as well. It had caramel color in it, though. I prefer to use products without added coloring. So, I won't get it again. If you aren't funny about added colors, you will love this stuff!

title: Love the stuff! Great price, too.
description: I have been using a the Senseo for several years now. Love the coffee. I just can not drink regular coffee out of a coffee pot anymore; it tastes gross to me now. This is a GREAT PRODUCT at a GREAT PRICE.

title: Love the stuff! Great price, too.
description: I have been using a the Senseo for several years now. Love the coffee. I just can not drink regular coffee out of a coffee pot anymore; it tastes gross to me now. This is a GREAT PRODUCT at a GREAT PRICE.

description: the gluten free stuff was very much appreciated by my brother in law who was having a hard time finding gluten free in his town

title: This is a great mix.
description: My wife uses this mix to make me bread and rolls. The rolls are baked in sheet metal rings (3 inch and 4 inch) that I made. This makes very nice  round rolls.

title: Chicken allergies
description:
I have a cat with chronic ear infections due to a food allergy. I have tried every brand from Iams to Evo and this is the one food that cleared her right up....

5 stars and thank god I finally found her food. 10 years of suffering seems to be over

title: Love Love Love
description: Found this tea in a local Asian store for about twice the price. I was pleased to find it here @ such a bargain. This is by far the best green tea I have ever had & trust me I've had a lot. Just steep though for a min or two max otherwise can get bitter.

title: Tastes Great!
description: It works and the taste is very pleasing. I will order again to get through those occasional sleepy afternoons. Works faster than a cup of coffee.

title: Great soup
description: This is a great tasting product. Cannot find it in major supermarkets anymore. Happy to find it online. Highly recommend it.

title: LOVE THESE COOKIES
description: I love crisp sugar cookies, these were perfect, tasted like regular gluten cookies.  Will buy over and over.

title: Better than wheat
description: My kids who are on a GF diet loves these.  My daughter who isn't on a GF diet says they taste better than wheat pretzels.  I'm not a pretzel lover myself, but I do ocassionally like to eat these.  I divide them into 3 baggies to cut down on the calories.

title: Great noodles
description:
Foremost: ~99% soluble fiber is great for you.

These noodles will-not get soft. I would not recommend for marinara sauce of any type. These noodles are made for stir fry type dishes. I did not feel they were rubbery at all. Make sure you blanch (toss in boiling water for a few minutes) before eating them.

Overall, just ordered more. Taste? There is none to the noodles themselves; though they don't smell nicely right out of the bag ( you are supposed to rinse then blanch).

title: GREAT! Main use is not soley for beverages
description:
How we use milk powder:
We use this milk powder in our coffee instead of artificial creamers; cold milk typically makes coffee.. well... cold!

Milk powder is great for low-fat / non-fat baking when the ingredient calls for milk but oil has already been substituted for apple sauce; cuts back on the liquid.

Protein shakes! Many low-carb protein powders can be converted into creamy meal replacements with 1/4cup of milk powder!

Many more ways to use it...

description: These cookies are the absolute treat for someone who likes light, fruity snacks. The waffles are airy and the filling is sweet and fragrant with a hint of acidity. They are very light and never filling. Delicious!

It solved all of his digestive problems; his weight is getting back to normal and his coat is shiny.  He feels better too - lots of energy, doesn't have to potty as often, etc.  Really happy I found a dogfood that is so ge

description: I love this brand of gluten free gravy mixes.  They taste good and it makes things taste great.  By purchasing in bulk it is less expensive than those on the average grocery store.

title: gluten free gravy mix for anyone
description: I love this brand of gluten free gravy mixes.  They taste good and it makes things taste great.  By purchasing in bulk it is less expensive than those on the average grocery store.

title: liquid beef broth concentrate
description: I love this liquid beef broth concentrate!  It is handy to have if you are sick and need nourishment; or,,,,what I use it most for is to add flavor to other foods.  Left over meat? use 1 or 2 packet(s) with 1(2) cup(s) water and heat the meat up and make gravy with the juice.  I will often use the beef broth with chicken for a unique flavor.  I add it to quinoa for beef flavoring.  We don't often use rice; but, it surely could be used for rice dishes as well.  I have a decent stock of this....ea

title: corn flakes gluten free
description: Who would ever think corn flakes need to be gluten free for some people?  Well, being on this special diet has made me aware!  This brand of cornflakes is delicious and I purchase in quantity because I use cornflakes for many things.  Nice to have something safe and delicious to eat at a reasonable cost.  Hope they never change their recipe....can't fix what isn't broken..

title: Bob's Red Mill non-fat dry milk powder
description: I purchased this to use for cooking; but tried a cup of this milk to drink at room temperature to get the taste so I could plan my recipes better.  I was very surprised!  It actually tasted good; even not cold.  I also tried this milk on my great-niece and she absolutely loved it!  This is one I will use for a long time....just don't change what don't need fixing,okay Bob's Red Mill?

title: These make the tails wag!
description: My dogs really like these treats.  They each get 1 (sometimes 2) after supper.  When they hear the box being opened (which I do very quietly) they come from wherever they are and sit very nicely with an expectant look on their faces.  I feel good knowing that these treats are healthy and low fat. Some of these treats are fairly large and would have to be broken up for a small dog. The 6 pack is a good buy and when I open the last box, I know that it is time to reorder.

title: Really Good Coffee
description: Bought a French Press coffee maker for my husband which requires trying the hundreds of different coffee beans available to find just the right blend.  He tried several, which were okay, and then I found this great deal of Cafe Altura Organic Peruvian Dark coffee on Amazon.  Figured I would try it to see if he liked it - which he did.  Think he might just stick with this brand for awhile. He likes strong coffee with a robust flavor, and this blend makes him happy in the morning.

title: Good Coffee
description:
This 3 pack of Taster's Choice was a good deal - better than I could do locally. If the price on the next auto-ship is
equally as good, I will continue to purchase it through Amazon.
Have been drinking Taster's Choice for many years and still enjoy the convenience and flavor.
And, in this economy with prices on just about everything continuing to go up, I am pleased to pay a reasonable price for a product that I enjoy.

title: Tofu Shirataki
description: The product is an excellent simulation of pasta.  I followed the instructions and prepared with sauce.  I did have a problem with delivery and though I was promised it would arrive two to four days after I placed the order, I waited for nearly three weeks and had to e-mail the seller to find out where it was.

title: Great Seasoning
description: Very good seasoning to add to your kitchen.  Use it on popcorn, cottage cheese or vegetables. We split a zucchini and put the seasoning on it for a special treat.  We keep this in our kitchen at all times.

title: Good Things
description: This product is better that anything I have ever used, yet it is not advertised as much, it is a wonder in a bottle, my family is very happy I bought it. I can't seem to find it in my local supermarket.

title: Pamela's wheat and gluten free bread mix
description: We've been using this product for my son with many allergies for almost 1.5 years.  As the manufacture says, it's wheat and gluten free.  My wife makes cakes, waffles, and breads.  And my son always loves it.  Now Amazon has a periodically delivered program with a good discount.  We'll keep purchasing it from Amazon and using it for my son.

title: Our Dogs Love Them
description: Our dogs love these fortune cookies. And the fortunes inside make for a bit of fun for us too.

title: Sweet and Delicious!
description:
I've often said that the Japanese have some of the most interesting snack foods - and this one doesn't disappoint! A soft marshmallow surrounds a thick paste that tastes very much like a flan-style pudding. It's very sweet, but then it says 'marshmallow' and 'pudding' - sweet should be expected.

Very nice treat - I wish I had ordered more!

title: Much better than rice or pasta
description: This is a must for dieters to get the feeling of satiety with no extra calories or carbs.  I think Miracle is a good description.  Amazon has the best price I've found and you'll want to buy enough to take advantage of the free shipping!

title: Hairball remedy
description: Product works really well on hairball problems and my cat will come back to get more if she's constipated and it seems to take care of that problem also.

title: Our 2 Cats love it!
description:
Our two cats are strange ! One loves the gravy so much she goes to the other cats dish to clean it right up, while the bigger cat eats her own fish plus the other cats fish. They also dine on Seafood Sensations dry food during the day.
We used to buy this item at our local Safeway store, it went from 69 cents a can to almost a dollar. Now buying it with the subscription every other month we are down to just 56 cents a can with Free delivery.

title: Love Baja Bob's!
description: This is awesome.  Pair it with Bacardi Big Apple rum and you've got a Appletini to die for, without the harshness of vodka nor the sugar of Pucker.  My kids love to mix it with sprite and have Sour Apple soda.  I also used it to make ice cubes to put in our Appletini's, which turned out awesome.  We always have this at our home bar, I never run out.  I'm addicted to Baja Bob's pre-mixed margarita mix, so if you haven't tried that yet, be sure you do!

title: Sweet!
description: Three family members tried the tablets with lemons, limes, pickle juice, etc.  You could pick up a lemon and eat it like you were eatting an orange.  It was definitely sweet, yet not sweet like drinking lemonade.  You have to try them to see what it's like!

title: Like a drug!
description:
Several in each pack.
Amazing taste.
Amazing supply.
Pure bliss.

These are actually rare in my neighborhood and my father and I LOVE them. I bought a box for his birthday and they quickly disappeared. I believe there's three sticks per pack, but man- they go quick. You can easily chomp down one after another, they don't fill you and the flavor- OH the flavor.

Seriously... these things are amazing. The packaging is nothing to complain about, neither is the dis

title: Delicious!
description:
Honestly, it's unfair to review these negatively.
Don't buy a feces sandwich if you don't like the taste of poo.
That's all I can say.

The seller I ordered from sent me a bag of many beans. A pound of buttered popcorn jellybeans just for me. They're soft, chewy and pack one heck of a punch of flavor.

So, if you enjoy this flavor, buy them. Don't if you're going to complain about how you willingly bought something you don't enjoy.

title: Dark, Rich, Clear Decaf!
description: I would have tried this coffee because it is from one of the most beautiful places on earth, the crisp, clear mountains of British Columbia.  This coffee is the best decaf I have ever tasted.  Often decaf tastes like it has a chemical aftertaste, (and some use chemicals in the processing), and some just lack that full bodied flavor.  This one which has its caffeine extracted with mountain water is the richest, most satisfying decafs ever.  You'll also feel great about yourself since it is fair t

title: THESE ARE AMAZING!!!
description: These are amazing and I can't imagine why they would be discontinued by the Ginger People. Any time I walked into a health food store and saw these, I'd buy them out. I use to eat the regular ginger chews until a friend had me try these... I was BLOWN away and they ARE addictive... IN A GOOD WAY!!!!!

title: Kraft Tangy Spaghetti Dinner
description: Kraft Tangy Spaghetti Dinners have been around since I was a kid and I am a retired senior citizen now. They are becoming increasingly harder to find. They are a delicious, easy quick fix dinner. I was thrilled to find them at Amazon and will continue to purchase them when available.

title: Souper Good
description: Today was a chilly September day, and I just canned tomato sauce yesterday, so it was a perfect day to try out my Bob's Red Mill Soup Mix. I was pleased that it cooked fairly quickly, one hour total, and was perfect and ready to eat. The tomato sauce added good flavor, and I threw in a little browned hamburger as well. There's a good recipe idea on the bag--after it's done cooking, put in one part milk to three parts soup, and warm it up before eating--but don't boil. I'll trying this next time.

title: Awesome stuff!
description: Great idea; don't know why someone didn't come up with this sooner! All the taste and protein of regular peanut butter with a third of the calories. I mix it with milk and cereal, protein powder, and jelly so far. Have more ideas to still try!

title: Great rich taste
description: This is a deeper, richer, more gingery and rooty tasting ginger ale than you might be used to.  Give it a try!  I love it and it makes other ginger ales seem tasteless and watery.  The diet version doesn't taste diet-y.  Also, Vernors for some reason keeps its fizziness longer than other sodas even after you've put ice in it.  If you like ice cream, vanilla ice cream in Vernors makes a really awesome ice cream soda.  Now I want one and I don't have any more Vernors!

title: Great Chili...
description: it's so good, that I decided to order it by the case from Amazon, instead of individually from the local grocery store.  Same outstanding quality, just a bit less expensive per box, and delivered to my door - no tax either.  If you like Chili, this is good stuff - I make my recipe in the crock-pot, and it's always a crowd pleaser.

title: Grove Square Hot Coco K-Cups
description: The Grove Square Hot Coco K-Cups have a good flavor but I find that the k-cups do not have enough hot coco mix to make that perfect cup. Thus I recommend putting a little less water in order to make each cup just right.

Pound for pound it would be cheaper to fly Mamacita in from Mexico so you could experience the real deal.  Sorry no sale at these prices.

Higgins & Burke's chai doesn't have any nasty licorice-y flavors in it, so hooray! It's a tasty chai that's heavier on clove and cardamom, and I really enjoy drinking it with a bit of vanilla soy milk.

I particularly like that it includes orzo pasta instead of the usual macaroni or shells that you so often see in boxed one-skillet meals. The flavoring is good and the signature Velveeta cheese adds a delicious creaminess to the dish.

Since we live in Florida we put it in the refrigerator otherwise the heat would make it quite runny.

title: Spree
description: They tasted great! They came quickly and in a huge bag and I loved eating them. I shared them with class mates and loved them also.

title: Great, but occasionally crushed
description: Very good product,it helps our (completely) indoor cats to maintain a healthy weight.  They like it and eat it well.  HOWEVER, based on ordering at least 30 cases, you should expect at least one can per case to be so crushed as to be unusable.  Two or three other cans per case will be dented, but usable.  As the outside packages arrive in good shape the damage must be occuring prior to shipment.

title: German wife: It's close
description: I think this bread is terrific!  It has great flavor and texture.  My German wife loves it too.  She says it is very close to what her mother would send her to pick up at the baker before WW II.  It is kind of rough for making sandwiches, however.

title: Ghost chili in a can, great item
description: Please do not listen to the writers who had bad experiences. These seeds in cans are a good product, but additional information will help you to be successful. I have purchased a dozen of these cans and I have gotten plants from every can. You must be patient and keep the cans in a warm area of your house. I keep the can under a grow light and near a heat vent to keep it warm. The seeds do not need light to sprout but warmth helps a lot. Experts say ideal is for the dirt to be 80-90 degrees F. G

title: All Grills should have a Grill Alert Talking Remote Meat Thermometer
description:
The Grill Thermometer is the best product i've ever ordered. Also well worth the small price. Your savings will be in the first months use. I use to burn most of my grill meat. Now its near
perfect.

title: Introduce a wide variety of flavors now
description: I am a big fan of Sprout baby foods and so is my 6 month old son. We started with stage 1 but quickly went on to the yummy combinations of the stage 2 foods. The flavors all work so well together and I believe I am expanding my son's palet now so he's more likely to accept and like a wide variety of foods and flavors as he gets older. The beans with mint is a unique and welcomed twist on an otherwise tough veggie to get infants to eat.  If you MUST you can always add just a small pinch of sugar.

title: Great Product and Even Better Design
description:
Having turned the product over to the women-folk for their analysis, it received a positive review. I honestly don't know much about shampoo and usually just use the soap from the dispenser at the gym, so my level of expertise in this area is less than zero.
However, they like it for several reasons. First, it seems they like the over quality, fragrance, and all that stuff. Second, the design is great. The bottle can be stored with the tab at the bottom so that you don't have to shake the l

title: Great Value, Ingredients and Taste
description:
First, at 12oz per bottle, you've got plenty of wow per squeeze. It works out to be about $6 a bottle, which is really a great deal. The vitamin C and just enough caffeine (40) really gives you a `gentle' boost instead of the wall-climbing-overdose followed by a big crash. It still tastes great even with zero calories.
I seriously like this a lot. Can't wait to try the others, esp. peach.

title: Great Idea, Improved Packaging
description:
Some products really catch my attention, and this is one of them. Antioxidants are nice but that's not the coolest part.

The sweetener is more concentrated than the stuff you buy in the bag, and like its yellow package brother, a very nice alternative to sugar.

The packaging is what I really like. The thicker foil packaging is great. It is vacuum sealed and water `resistant'. For camping, and other activities where you need to toss a couple packs in your bag, this is the ti

title: Great taste, low cal
description:
Always on the lookout for a good non-sugar substitute (or high fructose corn syrup) not necessarily because of calories but sugar has never appealed to me. And, I can't stand HFCS.
Stevia tastes very sweet and can easily be the next big thing in sweeteners. As the price continues to drop, keep an eye on this product. This is still a bit pricey and stevia proves worthwhile as a beverage sweeter with limited use in foods.
When the price comes down a bit more I'll be switching to stevia f

title: My favorite cracker
description: A cracker that is actually satisfying to eat alone or with cheese. It has substance, not like eating air, and it is subtely flavored so not to overpower cheese.

title: you should see my cat jump for these!!
description: my cat is 13 years old and had stopped cleaning himself - his pretty white fur was looking tan!  with these vitamins, not only is he keeping himself sparkling white, but he frisks like a kitten.  and he loves the taste - if i go for the cupboard where i keep them, then he runs over and meows insistantly.  what a great product.

title: GREAT product
description: I have used pill pockets for several years now. I am a pet sitter and have 4 dogs of my own, so there is always medicine to be given. I used to have to push a pill down my dogs throat. Now, they think they are getting a treat. They are :0) :0) Amazon is the best price I have found and even better because I get free shipping.

description: I'm a big fan of good jerky; made plenty of my own, and this stuff is great.  It's a little pricey, but the quality and flavor are worth it.  It is on the sweet side, but that's to be expected hence the name "sweet n' spicy".  You won't be disappointed. I couldn't keep my hands off the 8 bags and scarfed them down in 4 days--dirty gluttonous pig!

Although more expensive than most pasta, the price is also good relative to what you will have to pay for it if you buy it at Whole Foods for at least $1 more per package.  If you use the auto ship feature, you save even more money.

description:
Excellent tasting. Will have to remember to order some more later.

title: bit expensive but best tasting instant potato there is
description: Very easy to mix, done in seconds and most of people will not tell the difference between these and the real thing. These are great when you do not have the time to make them from scratch. These are not flakes, and do not taste like flakes.

title: shame on you FDA
description: this is the best known naturally occuring sweetener known to man, I use it for all my drinks tea-cool-aid and even in mixed drinks works great no glycimic index or calories no carbs and no side effects. this brand has left absolutly no aftertaste for me or anyone else who had it. also find a very tiny spoon like the old mcdonalds stirrers and if you sprikle it it slowly and evenly over the drink it will dissolve on its own, dont let it clump or you will have to stir a bit harder, just my thought

description: Since leaving Canada...I have missed one thing: Tim Hortons. I missed ordering a french cap and tasting its sweetness. You would not believe how happy I am to have found this and to have it available in the USA. I cannot taste a big difference between this and the real thing. Perfect for the cold winters of South Carolina. (Just kidding, the winters here are 60 degrees F). Seriously, if you like Tim Hortons french cappuccino, this will make your day.

title: Well, I liked it.
description:
I bought this as a joke between a friend and I, but when I tasted it, it turns out that I actually really liked it.
It's obviously not for everyone, because everyone has different food preferences, but I found it very good and may just buy another if the mood strikes.
Just saying, don't knock it until you've tried it.

title: pretty good, could use some work on the taste
description: i like the idea behind this product. Slow burning carbs, sustained energy. And it does provide just that. However, the taste is a little iffy. Its not horrible, but i have tasted other bars that are much better. The savior in these bars is the chunks of berries that are contained throughout, as they provide a balance to the not so good tasting stuff inbetween. Either way, these are healthy, good for you, and if the company can work on the taste, i would give them 5 starts.

title: Good Product from a Great Company
description:
I am a big fan of Bob's Red Mill products, which encouraged me to purchase these cranberries. While the price is a little high, they make themselves up in terms of quality.

I enjoy putting these in my cereals, just munching on a few here and there as a snack, and they really shine in baking for thing like muffins and breads. They taste really good are aren't too 'tart', and are an healthy alternative snack compared to all the other junk food out there.

title: Best Manuka Honey

I highly recommend this toy if you have a dog that loves to chew.

If I need Honey Toasted, I can run down to my local grocer and buy one bar to satisfy the craving.  These are great snack bars, with a good amount of fiber and whole grain, not to mention protein.

It is a great tea for you to try if you want to experience it for yourself and the price is GREAT!

title: Gone in a flash

title: Good flavor delivers a nice morning jolt.

I tried Vitamin Squeeze this morning as an alternative to my usual caffeinated and carbonated morning beverage. It has a nice fruit punch flavor, and very little after taste. I followed the directions of one squirt per eight ounces of water, and was rewarded with a light flavor that was not overpowering. I imagine that you could increase your squirts if you wanted more fruity goodness, but one squirt seemed about right for me.

Vitamin Squeeze was a good eye opener for the morning,

title: Herbal Unwind Tea
